{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a4e14af6cd","title":"现状再也不能忍了","origin":"《云南省高等学校右派分子反动言论选集》(中国共产党云南省高等学校委员会办公室编印，1957.8.15)，内部资料。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"04a0a8ee75","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":9,"articleId":"a4e14af6cd"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5286ee2e77","name":"乐麟祥"},{"id":"fc111585d0","name":"昆明师范学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f668e055af","type":"title","text":"现状再也不能忍了","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"4a36b1820a","type":"authors","text":"昆明师范学院学生乐麟祥","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"eea9d5ad81","type":"subtitle","text":"(乐麟祥：昆明师范学院物理专修科学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"0da729bbab","type":"paragraph","text":"我们这辈青年遭遇惨，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"de974ae1f7","type":"paragraph","text":"解放以来党员压在头上，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"bdea0e066d","type":"paragraph","text":"儿童生活的精神就受摧残，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"89cd1dc887","type":"paragraph","text":"历年来满腹的不满不敢讲，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"f59ab259b3","type":"paragraph","text":"实际上国家的一切报刊杂志上，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"13188376cb","type":"paragraph","text":"民主、自由、游行、示威的字样，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"d9f288f5f2","type":"paragraph","text":"只不过把一党专政说得冠冕堂皇，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"881bdfa52c","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主集中制”只要尾巴不要头，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"fa68066232","type":"paragraph","text":"社会上的一切现象只是几个党员，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"8549388493","type":"paragraph","text":"老爷强制包办，并且还要大吹大擂；","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ea405cb36d","type":"paragraph","text":"在我们的国家里充满自由和阳光，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"1a10f7c46a","type":"paragraph","text":"到处都有青年施展才能的地方，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"1bb0a6c184","type":"paragraph","text":"我历年来的观察只不过是共产党员的统治，没有得到民主“自由”的保障，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"0d288bed87","type":"paragraph","text":"从来我就体会不到党为我们争来什么样的自由和民主，我也不知觉为我们创造啥样的幸福好时光。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"e8ad0a3a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"党所标榜的这一切我一点也没有，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"a224c38283","type":"paragraph","text":"我有的是饥饿与冷寒痛苦和悲伤，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"38b795c75e","type":"paragraph","text":"我有的是辛酸的眼泪，反正时间有的是：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"c3cc4b9b6c","type":"paragraph","text":"恐怖和不安，吓得人终夜不安，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ed8616ef6e","type":"paragraph","text":"眠而又惊醒，饮食难下咽，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"88601ad4fa","type":"paragraph","text":"坐在课堂不讲什么样，我辈青年真遭殃，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"527e0d8025","type":"paragraph","text":"条条绳绑在身上，层层建筑压得气难喘，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"a17c9905cf","type":"paragraph","text":"无能的领导脑袋发了热，要求我们全面发展，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"94083b9a90","type":"paragraph","text":"五花八门要你学好，马上变为万灵丹，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"c9fe1bed48","type":"paragraph","text":"尤其政治思想和改造，不提它还好，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"7d65d4f39b","type":"paragraph","text":"提起给人带来极大的苦恼，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ad2d005438","type":"paragraph","text":"历年来在知识分子的头上","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"d93385518d","type":"paragraph","text":"“落后”“消极”反动的大帽子","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"2733f6f593","type":"paragraph","text":"满天飞舞叫人发慌，扑灭青年的科学高举的热情，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ff94146ad1","type":"paragraph","text":"磨平了棱角窒息了愿望，胆心的服服帖帖听使唤，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"72f5c97698","type":"paragraph","text":"不服的屁也不敢放，只有少数的猛士敢于揭穿你们的秘密，掀起群众反对现实的巨浪，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"c5c189b70f","type":"paragraph","text":"挣得了今天的鸣和放，我们这辈青年真可惨，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"e585b5fc31","type":"paragraph","text":"不早不迟降生于动乱不安的地方，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"467d784a09","type":"paragraph","text":"都拿我们来做实验的牺牲品，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"7d977a07c5","type":"paragraph","text":"口笑起伏如波浪，文教政策好比儿戏样，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"4e3bbd791e","type":"paragraph","text":"返来复去不断改，不知改磨了我们的多少好时光，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"957f1aa77b","type":"paragraph","text":"细心想想真气愤，虚度年华为那端，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"860dbb91f8","type":"paragraph","text":"只因党员团员挖沟筑城墙，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"cc033f910b","type":"paragraph","text":"只因到处“阶级出身”，说不象样，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"0091ffd89e","type":"paragraph","text":"只因你们打击“歧视”非党员，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"945ae36034","type":"paragraph","text":"只因你们强求所有的人都一样，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"5d5272ea2b","type":"paragraph","text":"只因肃反当中搞得太冤枉，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"c903079319","type":"paragraph","text":"只因你们血口喷人还说“好心肠”，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"afe56d0f16","type":"paragraph","text":"只因你们作事无天良，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"08819f9b3d","type":"paragraph","text":"这些原因那能使人心平意满，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"70cd969871","type":"paragraph","text":"这种现象怎能叫人安心苦赞，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"aef1d01b6e","type":"paragraph","text":"这样的现实再不变，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"d5345ca67e","type":"paragraph","text":"中华民族的前途不堪设想，","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"d238000251","type":"paragraph","text":"“科学进军”要变成空谈，","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"911307b17f","type":"paragraph","text":"社会依然还是黑暗，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"5e40bc1ff1","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的命运真是说不完，","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"52d67d2108","type":"paragraph","text":"走到那里都有老爷管，","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"978c466b76","type":"paragraph","text":"“批评”，叫人伤心不完，","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"359d96be12","type":"paragraph","text":"只许喷人不许争辩，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"a3172f87e7","type":"paragraph","text":"只许“领导”放火，不准百姓申冤，","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"616a7c095b","type":"paragraph","text":"谁要不满就是“反革命”，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"0a77d01797","type":"paragraph","text":"谁要自由讲话也是“反革命”，","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"bc3573dd56","type":"paragraph","text":"谁要坚持公正的立场，","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"8461fafdb9","type":"paragraph","text":"就得请回家休养，","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"4b45d08fd0","type":"paragraph","text":"一切大权总揽在党员手上，","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"f9fb743ab8","type":"paragraph","text":"一切事情党员把持着干，","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"1298d000b6","type":"paragraph","text":"历年来的政策太黑暗，","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"9ea28f1fc6","type":"paragraph","text":"杀人易如杀鸡一样，","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"99b09255de","type":"paragraph","text":"其中多少的人被冤枉，","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"cfe4ab4c21","type":"paragraph","text":"甚至杀人不费一粒子弹，","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ea5dd9b5fd","type":"paragraph","text":"只是棒棍和枪筒，","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"3aaf8dc10e","type":"paragraph","text":"不计其数的打死在场上，","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ae22f796e0","type":"paragraph","text":"请问你们的良心是什么样，","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"1ecec21247","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的心肠里如这般，","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"4702abcca8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们高唱的“人道”不好讲，","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"bbf4a6613e","type":"paragraph","text":"到如今“个别”“缺点”“错误”再也不能把你们的罪恶来抵尝，","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"9afade2b40","type":"paragraph","text":"我们再也不能听信骗人的叫喊，","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"9d8d5bf71a","type":"paragraph","text":"我冤受曲的青年们！","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"79cf076e12","type":"paragraph","text":"一道来掀掉头上的大石板，","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"4741d758a1","type":"paragraph","text":"拨开乌云见太阳，","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"c939f501ce","type":"paragraph","text":"用沸腾的热血争取自身的彻底解放，","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"e8ebda5117","type":"paragraph","text":"以愤怒的眼泪冲去党员的专制黑暗。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"fa6491bd45","type":"paragraph","text":"唾弃官僚老爷们，鞭走身旁的小侦探，","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"51c0945c16","type":"paragraph","text":"摆脱统治和压迫，","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"9b4ced2f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"消灭不合理的现象，","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"56f5c82091","type":"paragraph","text":"踏着四烈士的血迹，为争取民主自由平等贡献我们的力量！","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"},{"id":"ca0db35d90","type":"paragraph","text":" 鸣者于6月9日","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd"}],"page":{"id":"ffd12bd63f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a4e14af6cd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}